   "id": "05b5d13d-c437-4b29-8a6d-64d7897989a0",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Introduction\n",
    "\n",
    "The food and restaurant industry has experienced significant growth in recent years, with online platforms such as Zomato making it easier for customers to discover restaurants, read reviews, compare ratings, and place online orders. The large amount of customer and restaurant data available on these platforms provides valuable insights into consumer preferences and restaurant trends.\n",
    "\n",
    "The objective of this project is to perform Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) on the Bengaluru Zomato Restaurant Dataset. Through data cleaning, visualization, and statistical analysis, this project aims to understand restaurant distribution, customer ratings, pricing patterns, cuisine preferences, online ordering trends, and table booking services. The insights generated from this analysis can help identify important characteristics of Bengaluru's restaurant market and customer behavior.\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "id": "911cc252-ee38-4463-a207-c18ac3aa4b1c",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
